war veterans who continued to harass, intimidate and kill its
members, seriously disrupting farming operations.
</P>
<P>
The war veterans have occupied about 1,500 white-owned farms
since February to force the government to speed up the land
redistribution program.
</P>
<P>
The Zimbabwean government has targeted 804 white farms for
compulsory acquisition to resettle landless peasants.
</P>
<P>
Hunzvi told the news agency that the strike by white commercial
farmers was aimed at economic sabotage and derailing the
government's land redistribution program.
</P>
<P>
"They are reactionaries who want to destabilize economy. As war
veterans we will not allow them to hold the nation at ransom," he
said. 
