drunk hooligans ripped out seats, lit flares and threw them onto
the pitch with the intention of causing a major incident."
</P>
<P>
The fans retaliated by ripping out seats and throwing them at
police, who were forced to retreat. They stormed back into the
crowd 15 minutes after the interval as reinforcements arrived to
quell the violence.
