agent responsible for transporting livestock and frozen meat from
the mainland to Hong Kong, announced Thursday its Sheung Shui
Slaughterhouse has been awarded ISO14001 environmental management
certification by Britain's Lioyd's register Quality Assurance.
</P>
<P>
The slaughterhouse, among some 70 Hong Kong enterprises, was
the first food manufacturing and processing enterprise in Hong
Kong to receive the world-recoganized environmental management
accreditation from Lioyd's, said Chen Shulin, Chairman of Ng Fung
Hong Limited.
</P>
