hygiene and environmental requirements to food processing industry,
" Chen said, adding that the commissioning of the Sheung Shui
Slaughterhouse "only marked the beginning" of their environment-
friendly operations.
</P>
<P>
Ng Fung Hong Limited plays an important role in Hong Kong
people's life for its three express trains which arrive in
Shenzhen every day to transport livestock, frozen meat and
vegetable from the mainland to Hong Kong. 
