autonomous regions of Xinjiang, Ningxia, Gansu, Qinghai and
Shaanxi will establish regional cooperative ties on the basis of
mutual benefit geared to the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
They will bring their respective advantages into full play for
joint development.
</P>
<P>
The meeting is called at a time when China has carrying out a
strategy to develop the vast but underdeveloped western region on
a large scale as the reform and opening-up policy has greatly
promoted development in the eastern coastal area over the past
more than two decades.  
