mandate, works in the framework of constitution. He should be able
to complete his mandate," said Robertson.
</P>
<P>
Montenegro recently rejected a constitutional amendment voted
by the Yugoslav parliament, which allows Yugoslav President
Milosevic have one more year of presidential mandate after it
expires next year.
</P>
<P>
Robertson will begin on Thursday a visit to France, the current
rotating presidency state of the European Union, to discuss issues
of European defense. 
