providing Chinese minors with information about the dangers of
drugs, sexually-transmitted diseases, AIDS and unexpected
pregnancy.
</P>
<P>
Chen Yiyun, professor with the Institute of Sociology under the
Chinese Academy of Social Sciences, and Hu Peicheng, secretary-
