<HEADLINE> Estrada Orders Deployment of 7,000 Militiamen in Mindanao </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, July 27 (Xinhua) -- Philippine President Joseph Estrada
has ordered the activation of 10,000 militiamen effective next
month even as the military starts its rehabilitation campaign in
Central Mindanao, the military said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
