<HEADLINE> ASEAN's Security Forum Closes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Attending the 7th ASEAN Regional Forum (ARF) are 23 foreign
ministers: ten from the ASEAN members -- Brunei, Cambodia,
Indonesia, Laos, Malaysia, Myanmar, the Philippines, Singapore,
Thailand and Vietnam, and ten from its dialogue partners --
Australia, Canada, China, the European Union, India, Japan, New
Zealand, Russia, South Korea and the Untied State.
</P>
<P>
