manufacturing and marketing of pharmaceutical products at a
national conference on medical reform held in Shanghai Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
A medical insurance system for urban workers, as a key element
of the reform of state-owned enterprises and social security
system, will be initially completed by the end of this year to
provide people with cheaper but better medical services.
</P>
<P>
 China Daily
</P>
<P>
-- The U.S. Navy guided-missile cruiser USS Chancellorsville
will visit the port city of Qingdao in eastern China's Shandong
Province from August 2-5, a spokesperson of the Chinese Defense
Ministry said Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
-- China deeply regrets the failure of the Middle East peace
summit at Camp David and hopes that talks will restart, Foreign
