ashes in their church whose doors and windows were nailed shut in
Kanungu.
</P>
<P>
Hundreds of bodies were discovered in various places in the
country including the capital Kampala where the doomsday cult had
branches.
</P>
<P>
"There are no more possibilities of any more bodies being found.
There is nothing else, and we have searched everywhere," Mugenyi
said. 
