welcomed the formation of the new political party by Mwila, saying
the MMD had been expecting it for a long time.
</P>
<P>
Mwila lost his minister portfolio after he was expelled for the
country's ruling party earlier this month. He was suspended last
month by MMD National Secretary Michael Sata, who charged that in
the past 18 months, Mwila had been involved in anti-party
activities which greatly destabilized the party.
</P>
<P>
